  "texts": [
    "The reason we choose these two is that they have a relatively positive correlation to human judgements.",
    "For the other three metrics, firstly, BLEU shows NLLB as better for terms and concepts, which does not correspond to human judgement.",
    "More than that, BLEU shows WMT21fb concepts to be better than the Marian Helsinki model, which is completely incorrect.",
    "Secondly, COMET score for the NLLB model is higher than 1, which is clearly caused by the fact that this implementation of COMET was not normalised by the Sigmoid function.",
    "Also, this COMET score for NLLB is higher than the one for Marian Helsinki."
